47 template <typename T> class handle_traits {};
48 
62 template <typename T, typename traits=handle_traits<T>> class handle {
63 private:
64  static mkldnn_status_t dummy_destructor(T){ return mkldnn_success; }
65 
66  std::shared_ptr<typename std::remove_pointer<T>::type> _data;
67  handle(const handle &&) = delete;
68  handle &operator=(const handle &&other) = delete;
69 protected:
70  bool operator==(const T other) const { return other == _data.get(); }
71  bool operator!=(const T other) const { return !(*this == other); }
72 public:
76  handle(T t = 0, bool weak = false): _data(0) {
77  reset(t, weak);
78  }
79 
80  handle(const handle &other): _data(other._data) {}
81  handle &operator=(const handle &other) {
82  _data = other._data;
83  return *this;
84  }
88  void reset(T t, bool weak = false) {
89  _data.reset(t, weak ? &dummy_destructor : traits::destructor);
90  }
91 
93  T get() const { return _data.get(); }
94 
95  bool operator==(const handle &other) const { return other._data.get() == _data.get(); }
96  bool operator!=(const handle &other) const { return !(*this == other); }
97 };

428  void get_output_scales(int &mask, std::vector<float> &scales) const
429  {
430  mkldnn_dim_t count;
431  int c_mask;
432  const float *c_scales;
433  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_primitive_attr_get_output_scales(get(),
434  &count, &c_mask, &c_scales),
435  "could not get int output scales");
436  scales.resize(count);
437 
438  mask = c_mask;
439  for (mkldnn_dim_t c = 0; c < count; ++c)
440  scales[c] = c_scales[c];
441  }

446  (mkldnn_dim_t)scales.size(), mask, &scales[0]),
447  "could not set int output scales");
448  }

955  struct desc {
956  friend struct memory;
958  mkldnn_memory_desc_t data;
959 
961  desc(): data() {}
962 
968  desc(const dims &adims, data_type adata_type,
969  format_tag aformat) {
970  validate_dims(adims);
971  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_memory_desc_init_by_tag(&data, (int)adims.size(),
972  adims.size() == 0 ? nullptr : &adims[0],
973  convert_to_c(adata_type), convert_to_c(aformat)),
974  "could not initialize a memory descriptor");
975  }
976 
980  desc(const mkldnn_memory_desc_t &adata): data(adata) {}
981 
983  //
986  desc submemory_desc(const dims &adims, const dims &offsets) {
987  mkldnn_memory_desc_t sub_md;
988  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_memory_desc_init_submemory(&sub_md,
989  &data, &adims[0], &offsets[0]),
990  "could not initialize a sub-memory");
991  return desc(sub_md);
992  }
993 
996  size_t get_size() const { return mkldnn_memory_desc_get_size(&data); }
997 
998  bool operator==(const desc &other) const {
999  return mkldnn_memory_desc_equal(&data, &other.data) != 0;
1000  }
1001 
1002  bool operator!=(const desc &other) const { return !operator==(other); }
1003  };
1004 
1010  memory(const desc &md, const engine &aengine, void *ahandle) {
1011  mkldnn_memory_t result;
1012  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_memory_create(&result, &md.data,
1013  aengine.get(), ahandle), "could not create a memory");
1014  reset(result);
1015  }
1016 
1021  memory(const desc &md, const engine &aengine)
1022  : memory(md, aengine, MKLDNN_NATIVE_HANDLE_ALLOCATE) {}
1023 
1025  desc get_desc() const {
1026  const mkldnn_memory_desc_t *cdesc;
1027  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_memory_get_memory_desc(get(), &cdesc),
1028  "could not get memory descriptor from a memory");
1029  return desc(*cdesc);
1030  }
1031 
1033  engine get_engine() const {
1034  mkldnn_engine_t engine_q;
1035  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_memory_get_engine(get(), &engine_q),
1036  "could not get engine from a memory");
1037  return engine(engine_q);
1038  }
1039 
1043  void *get_data_handle() const {
1044  void *handle;
1045  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_memory_get_data_handle(get(), &handle),
1046  "could not get native handle");
1047  return handle;
1048  }
1049 
1050  void set_data_handle(void *handle) const {
1051  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_memory_set_data_handle(get(), handle),
1052  "could not set native handle");
1053  }
1054 
1063  template <typename T = void>
1064  T *map_data() const {
1065  void *mapped_ptr;
1066  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_memory_map_data(get(), &mapped_ptr),
1067  "could not map the data");
1068  return static_cast<T *>(mapped_ptr);
1069  }
1070 
1076  void unmap_data(void *mapped_ptr) const {
1077  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_memory_unmap_data(get(), mapped_ptr),
1078  "could not unmap the data");
1079  }
1080 
1081 #if MKLDNN_WITH_OPENCL

1083  cl_mem mem_object;

1085  "could not get OpenCL memory object");

1091  "could not set OpenCL memory object");

1093 #endif

1095  // Must go away or be private:

1097  return static_cast<mkldnn_data_type_t>(adata_type);
1098  }

1100  return static_cast<mkldnn_format_tag_t>(aformat);

1138 struct reorder : public primitive {
1139  struct primitive_desc : public handle<mkldnn_primitive_desc_t> {
1140  primitive_desc(const engine &src_engine, const memory::desc &src_md,
1141  const engine &dst_engine, const memory::desc &dst_md,
1142  const primitive_attr &aattr) {
1143  mkldnn_primitive_desc_t result;
1144  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_reorder_primitive_desc_create(&result,
1145  src_engine.get(), &src_md.data,
1146  dst_engine.get(), &dst_md.data, aattr.get()),
1147  "could not create a reorder primitive descriptor");
1148  reset(result);
1149  }
1150 
1151  primitive_desc(const engine &src_engine, const memory::desc &src_md,
1152  const engine &dst_engine, const memory::desc &dst_md) {
1153  mkldnn_primitive_desc_t result;
1154  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_reorder_primitive_desc_create(&result,
1155  src_engine.get(), &src_md.data,
1156  dst_engine.get(), &dst_md.data, nullptr),
1157  "could not create a reorder primitive descriptor");
1158  reset(result);
1159  }
1160 
1161  primitive_desc(const memory &src, const memory &dst,
1162  const primitive_attr &aattr) {
1163  mkldnn_primitive_desc_t result;
1164  auto src_md = src.get_desc();
1165  auto dst_md = dst.get_desc();
1166  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_reorder_primitive_desc_create(&result,
1167  src.get_engine().get(), &src_md.data,
1168  dst.get_engine().get(), &dst_md.data, aattr.get()),
1169  "could not create a reorder primitive descriptor");
1170  reset(result);
1171  }
1172 
1173  primitive_desc(const memory &src, const memory &dst) {
1174  mkldnn_primitive_desc_t result;
1175  auto src_md = src.get_desc();
1176  auto dst_md = dst.get_desc();
1177  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_reorder_primitive_desc_create(&result,
1178  src.get_engine().get(), &src_md.data,
1179  dst.get_engine().get(), &dst_md.data, nullptr),
1180  "could not create a reorder primitive descriptor");
1181  reset(result);
1182  }
1183 
1184  memory::desc scratchpad_desc() const {
1185  const mkldnn_memory_desc_t *cdesc = mkldnn_primitive_desc_query_md(
1186  get(), mkldnn::convert_to_c(scratchpad_md), 0);
1187  if (cdesc == nullptr)
1188  return memory::desc();
1189  return memory::desc(*cdesc);
1190  }
1191 
1192  engine scratchpad_engine() {
1193  mkldnn_engine_t engine_q;
1194  error::wrap_c_api(
1195  mkldnn_primitive_desc_query(get(),
1196  mkldnn::convert_to_c(query_scratchpad_engine), 0, &engine_q),
1197  "could not get scratchpad engine from reorder primitive_desc");
1198 
1199  return engine(engine_q);

1363 
1365 struct primitive_desc : public handle<mkldnn_primitive_desc_t> {
1366  primitive_desc(const_mkldnn_op_desc_t desc, const primitive_attr *attr,
1367  const engine &e, const_mkldnn_primitive_desc_t hint_fwd_pd) {
1368  mkldnn_primitive_desc_iterator_t iterator = nullptr;
1369  mkldnn_status_t status = mkldnn_primitive_desc_iterator_create(
1370  &iterator, desc, attr ? attr->get() : nullptr, e.get(),
1371  hint_fwd_pd);
1372  error::wrap_c_api(status,
1373  "could not create a primitive descriptor iterator");
1374  pd_iterator.reset(iterator);
1375  fetch_impl();
1376  }
1377 
1378  engine get_engine() { return engine::query(*this); }
1379 
1380  primitive_attr get_primitive_attr() const {
1381  const_mkldnn_primitive_attr_t const_cattr;
1382  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_primitive_desc_get_attr(get(), &const_cattr),
1383  "could not get attributes");
1384  mkldnn_primitive_attr_t cattr;
1385  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_primitive_attr_clone(&cattr, const_cattr),
1386  "could not clone attributes");
1387 
1388  primitive_attr attr;
1389  attr.reset(cattr);
1390  return attr;
1391  }
1392 
1394  const char *impl_info_str() const {
1395  const char *res;
1396  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_primitive_desc_query(get(),
1397  mkldnn_query_impl_info_str, 0, &res),
1398  "could not query implementation info string");
1399  return res;
1400  }
1401 
1403  memory::dim query_s64(query q) const {
1404  memory::dim res;
1405  mkldnn_status_t status = mkldnn_primitive_desc_query(get(),
1406  mkldnn::convert_to_c(q), 0, &res);
1407  return status == mkldnn_success ? res : 0;
1408  }
1409 
1416  bool next_impl() {
1417  mkldnn_status_t status = mkldnn_primitive_desc_iterator_next(
1418  pd_iterator.get());
1419  if (status == mkldnn_iterator_ends) return false;
1420  error::wrap_c_api(status, "primitive descriptor iterator next failed");
1421 
1422  fetch_impl();
1423  return true;
1424  }
1425 
1427  memory::desc query_md(query what, int idx = 0) const {
1428  std::vector<query> valid_q{src_md, diff_src_md, weights_md,
1429  diff_weights_md, dst_md, diff_dst_md, workspace_md, scratchpad_md};
1430  if (!std::any_of(valid_q.cbegin(), valid_q.cend(),
1431  [=](query q) { return what == q; }))
1432  throw error(mkldnn_invalid_arguments, "invalid memory query");
1433 
1434  const mkldnn_memory_desc_t *cdesc = mkldnn_primitive_desc_query_md(
1435  get(), mkldnn::convert_to_c(what), idx);
1436  if (cdesc == nullptr) return memory::desc();
1437 
1438  return memory::desc(*cdesc);
1439  }
1440 
1441  // register specialized queries, e.g. src_desc()
1442 # define REG_QUERY_MD(name, what, idx) \
1443  memory::desc name ## _desc() const { return query_md(what ## _md, idx); }
1444 
1445  private:
1446  handle<mkldnn_primitive_desc_iterator_t> pd_iterator;
1447  void fetch_impl() {
1448  mkldnn_primitive_desc_t pd = mkldnn_primitive_desc_iterator_fetch(
1449  pd_iterator.get());
1450  error::wrap_c_api(pd != nullptr ? mkldnn_success : mkldnn_runtime_error,
1451  "could not fetch a primitive descriptor from the iterator");
1452  reset(pd);
1453  }
1454 };
